   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Three-site XXX_{su(2)} chain (L=3). Sites carry independent gl(2) representations [λ1,0],\n  [λ2,0], [λ3,0], independent inhomogeneities θ1, θ2, θ3, and a SHARED companion twist G=(χ1,χ2)\n  for the whole chain. Physical space V_λ1⊗V_λ2⊗V_λ3. Generator/GT-basis machinery (ps,dim,J0,\n  Jp,Jm,JJ) and Ee, L are ported verbatim from XXX_su2.wb — they are single-site building blocks,\n  independent of L. Structural difference from the L=2 notebook: t3[1,1](u) is CUBIC in u (three\n  Lax factors, not two), which changes the Baxter/TauEigensystem construction in Section B — see\n  the design note at the top of this notebook's implementation plan for the derivation.*)",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ps[rep_] :=\n  ps[rep] =\n   Block[{res = (Prepend[rep, #] & /@ (Tuples[\n          Table[Range[rep[[1, i + 1]], rep[[1, i]]], {i, 1,\n            Length[rep[[1]]] - 1}]]))},\n    If[Length[res[[1, 1]]] == 1, Reverse@Sort@res,\n     Reverse@Sort@Flatten[ps /@ res, 1]]];\ndim[rep_] := dim[rep] = Length[ps[{rep}]];\nJ0[k_][pat_] :=\n  J0[k][pat] =\n   Sum[pat[[k, i]], {i, 1, k}] - Sum[pat[[k - 1, i]], {i, 1, k - 1}];\nJp[k_][pat_] :=\n  Jp[k][pat] = -Sum[\n     Product[pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k + 1, j]] + j, {j,\n         Range[k + 1]}]/\n       Product[pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k, j]] + j, {j,\n         Complement[Range[k], {i}]}] v[\n       ReplacePart[pat, {k, i} -> pat[[k, i]] + 1]], {i, 1, k}];\nJm[k_][pat_] :=\n  Jm[k][pat] =\n   Sum[Product[\n       pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k - 1, j]] + j, {j, Range[k - 1]}]/\n      Product[pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k, j]] + j, {j,\n        Complement[Range[k], {i}]}] v[\n      ReplacePart[pat, {k, i} -> pat[[k, i]] - 1]], {i, 1, k}];\nJJ[k_, l_, rep_] :=\n  JJ[k, l, rep] =\n   Which[k == l, DiagonalMatrix[J0[k] /@ ps[{rep}]], l == k + 1,\n    Transpose[\n     Table[Coefficient[Jp[k][ps[{rep}][[i]]], v[#]] & /@\n       ps[{rep}], {i, 1, Length[ps[{rep}]]}]], l == k - 1,\n    Transpose[\n     Table[Coefficient[Jm[l][ps[{rep}][[i]]], v[#]] & /@\n       ps[{rep}], {i, 1, Length[ps[{rep}]]}]], l > k + 1,\n    JJ[k, k + 1, rep] . JJ[k + 1, l, rep] -\n     JJ[k + 1, l, rep] . JJ[k, k + 1, rep], l < k - 1,\n    JJ[k, k - 1, rep] . JJ[k - 1, l, rep] -\n     JJ[k - 1, l, rep] . JJ[k, k - 1, rep]];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "{dim[{1, 0}], dim[{2, 0}], dim[{3, 0}]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"598685\" data-output-id=\"121\" data-out-n=\"128\" data-sub-idx=\"0\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"4\" data-sub-start=\"0\" data-sub-end=\"0\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[128]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrma3gh3-j5k4aa6\" data-page-width-em=\"33\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezIsMyw0XHJpZ2h0XH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[128]= \\left\\{2,3,4\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "300f7f16-e6a5-43a0-bf7f-74feeacd98b3"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*spin-s generators*)\nClearAll[Ee];\nEe[λ_][i_,j_]:=JJ[i,j,{λ,0}]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Lax matrix for spin-s representation (no θ baked in — shift applied when a site is instantiated)*)\nClearAll[L];\nL[λ_][i_,j_][u_]:=KroneckerDelta[i,j]*u*IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ,0}]]-h Ee[λ][j,i];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "Dimensions[L[2][1, 1][u]]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"598685\" data-output-id=\"122\" data-out-n=\"133\" data-sub-idx=\"0\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"7\" data-sub-start=\"0\" data-sub-end=\"0\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[133]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrma3lwv-ey77arf\" data-page-width-em=\"33\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezMsM1xyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[133]= \\left\\{3,3\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "da51ae8a-dbd3-41b3-9bf8-b25d763b1d35"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*companion twist matrix — shared by the whole chain*)\nG={{χ1,-χ2},{1,0}};",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Three-site Lax operators on V_λ1⊗V_λ2⊗V_λ3, built as KroneckerProduct of the single-site Lax\n  matrix (evaluated at its own site's inhomogeneity shift) with the identity on the other two\n  factors. Signature L1[λ1,λ2,λ3][i,j][u], etc. — all three λ's must be supplied to each routine\n  even though only one representation enters the shifted Lax matrix itself, because the size of\n  the identity factors depends on the OTHER two sites' representations.*)",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[L1,L2,L3];\nL1[λ1_,λ2_,λ3_][i_,j_][u_]:=KroneckerProduct[L[λ1][i,j][u-θ1],IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ2,0}]],IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ3,0}]]];\nL2[λ1_,λ2_,λ3_][i_,j_][u_]:=KroneckerProduct[IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ1,0}]],L[λ2][i,j][u-θ2],IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ3,0}]]];\nL3[λ1_,λ2_,λ3_][i_,j_][u_]:=KroneckerProduct[IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ1,0}]],IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ2,0}]],L[λ3][i,j][u-θ3]];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "Dimensions[L1[1, 1, 1][1, 1][u]]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Monodromy matrix T[λ1,λ2,λ3][i,j][u] = product of the three site Lax operators in auxiliary\n  space, T(u)=L1(u).L2(u).L3(u). All three factors carry the SAME spectral parameter u — each\n  site's inhomogeneity shift is already built into L1/L2/L3 via θ1,θ2,θ3 respectively.*)",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[T];\nT[λ1_,λ2_,λ3_][i_,j_][u_]:=T[λ1,λ2,λ3][i,j][u]=Sum[L1[λ1,λ2,λ3][i,k][u].L2[λ1,λ2,λ3][k,l][u].L3[λ1,λ2,λ3][l,j][u],{k,2},{l,2}];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "Dimensions[T[1, 1, 1][1, 1][u]]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*transfer matrix in fundamental representation*)\nClearAll[t3];\nt3[λ1_,λ2_,λ3_][1,1][u_]:=Sum[T[λ1,λ2,λ3][i,j][u]G[[j,i]],{i,2},{j,2}];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*transfer matrices commute at different values of spectral parameter*)\n(*so coefficients generate a complete family of integrals of motion. Range kept to {1,2} (not\n  L2's {1,...,4}) to bound compute cost — dimension grows as (λ+1)^3 at three sites.*)\nTable[t3[λ1,λ2,λ3][1,1][u].t3[λ1,λ2,λ3][1,1][v]-t3[λ1,λ2,λ3][1,1][v].t3[λ1,λ2,λ3][1,1][u],{λ1,1,2},{λ2,1,2},{λ3,1,2}]//Simplify//Flatten//Union",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*NOTE: the symbolic Simplify//Flatten//Union above does not collapse to the literal list {0} —\n  the residual terms shown are combinations of exact rational coefficients with 30-digit-precision\n  κ1,κ2/χ1 numbers (e.g. \"0``28.8...+0``29.0...*I\"), which Simplify does not always merge into an\n  exact 0 when mixed with exact-rational polynomial pieces (this is a display/simplification\n  artifact of precision-tracked arithmetic, not evidence of a bug — see the notebook's precision\n  gotchas). Confirms the SAME commutator vanishes exactly (to Chop tolerance) at generic COMPLEX\n  numeric u,v, for every (λ1,λ2,λ3) in the same range — this is the substantive check.*)\nMax[Abs[Flatten[Table[(t3[λ1,λ2,λ3][1,1][u].t3[λ1,λ2,λ3][1,1][v]-t3[λ1,λ2,λ3][1,1][v].t3[λ1,λ2,λ3][1,1][u]) /. {u->N[1.234,30]+I N[0.567,30], v->N[5.678,30]-I N[2.345,30]},{λ1,1,2},{λ2,1,2},{λ3,1,2}]]]]//Chop",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"598685\" data-output-id=\"139\" data-out-n=\"211\" data-sub-idx=\"1\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"17\" data-sub-start=\"7\" data-sub-end=\"7\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[211]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrmah37r-zl0wacp\" data-page-width-em=\"33\" data-latex-b64=\"MA==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
