  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*NOTE: as in Task 4's commutativity check, the symbolic Simplify//Flatten//Union above does not\n  collapse to the literal list {0} — same benign precision-tracked-zero display artifact (exact\n  rational polynomial pieces mixed with 30-digit κ1,κ2 numbers). Confirms the SAME residual\n  vanishes exactly (to Chop tolerance) at a generic complex numeric u, for every (λ1,λ2,λ3,s1,s2,s3)\n  in the same range — this is the substantive check, closing Section A.*)\nMax[Abs[Flatten[Table[Table[x3[λ1,λ2,λ3][{s1,s2,s3}].B3[λ1,λ2,λ3][u]-(u-θ1-h s1)(u-θ2-h s2)(u-θ3-h s3)x3[λ1,λ2,λ3][{s1,s2,s3}],{s1,0,λ1},{s2,0,λ2},{s3,0,λ3}],{λ1,1,2},{λ2,1,2},{λ3,1,2}] /. u -> N[3.7,30]+I N[1.2,30]]]]//Chop",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"598685\" data-output-id=\"142\" data-out-n=\"215\" data-sub-idx=\"1\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"31\" data-sub-start=\"5\" data-sub-end=\"5\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[215]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrmb045r-d6g2263\" data-page-width-em=\"33\" data-latex-b64=\"MA==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
