  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Section B — Baxter (TQ) solver for L=3. Structural difference from L=2, validated in Task 5's\n  asymptotic cross-check above: t3[1,1](u) is CUBIC in u, so τ0(u) below carries only its u^3,u^2\n  terms (state-independent), and TWO free per-state numbers (J1,J0) are needed instead of L2's\n  single J — see TauEigensystem (Task 10) and QSolve (Task 11).*)",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*a(u), Qθ(u) (triple product; reuses the Qθ defined in Task 7 — no redefinition needed here since\n  Section B was never split from Section A into a separately self-contained file for L3), and\n  τ0 = the state-independent part of τ (using ee1=λ1+λ2+λ3-M, ee2=M). τ0 has ONLY u^3,u^2 terms by\n  construction — its u^1,u^0 coefficients are deliberately zero; the actual eigenvalue is\n  τ=τ0+J1 u+J0 with (J1,J0) read directly per state in TauEigensystem (Task 10).\n  qpoly builds a polynomial from an ASCENDING coefficient list {c0,...,cM} (cM=1 for monic q_n);\n  formed in a dummy symbol first so substituting uu=0 gives the constant term rather than an\n  indeterminate 0^0.*)\nClearAll[aFun, τ0, qpoly];\naFun[λ1_, λ2_, λ3_][u_] := (u - θ1 - h λ1) (u - θ2 - h λ2) (u - θ3 - h λ3);\nτ0[λ1_, λ2_, λ3_, M_][u_] := (κ1 + κ2) u^3 - (θ1 + θ2 + θ3) (κ1 + κ2) u^2 - u^2 h (κ1 (λ1 + λ2 + λ3 - M) + κ2 M);\nqpoly[clist_, uu_] := Module[{x}, (clist . x^Range[0, Length[clist] - 1]) /. x -> uu];\n{aFun[1, 1, 1][u], Qθ[u], τ0[1, 1, 1, 1][u]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"598685\" data-output-id=\"127\" data-out-n=\"170\" data-sub-idx=\"5\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"33\" data-sub-start=\"12\" data-sub-end=\"12\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[170]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrma67qa-2pi7n09\" data-page-width-em=\"34\" data-latex-b64=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.4em;vertical-align:-0.95em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">{</span></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">u</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3214em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">5</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">9</span></span></span></span