       "data": "Out[170]= \\left\\{\\left(u-\\frac{9}{5}\\right)\\,\\left(u-\\frac{4}{3}\\right)\\,\\left(u-\\frac{8}{7}\\right),\\left(u-\\frac{4}{5}\\right)\\,\\left(u-\\frac{1}{3}\\right)\\,\\left(u-\\frac{1}{7}\\right),\\left(0.720879750294453074533355301191+0.\\times 10^{-30}\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,u^3-\\left(2.00129949724602924977593400283+0.93278244859337471648483598207\\,\\mathrm{i}\\right)\\,u^2\\right\\}",
