  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* dPred[M,λ1,λ2,λ3]: predicted dimension of the weight-M subspace of Vλ1⊗Vλ2⊗Vλ3 (number of\n   (m1,m2,m3) triples with m1+m2+m3=M, 0<=mi<=λi) — a direct triple-convolution count (no closed\n   form; small ranges make the brute double-sum cheap). This is what the GENUINE\n   t3-diagonalization below (Task 10) must reproduce exactly for every M. *)\nClearAll[dPred];\ndPred[M_, λ1_, λ2_, λ3_] := Sum[If[0 <= M - m1 - m2 <= λ3, 1, 0], {m1, 0, λ1}, {m2, 0, λ2}];\n{Sum[dPred[M, 1, 1, 1], {M, 0, 3}], dim[{1, 0}] dim[{1, 0}] dim[{1, 0}]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"598685\" data-output-id=\"130\" data-out-n=\"179\" data-sub-idx=\"3\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"36\" data-sub-start=\"6\" data-sub-end=\"6\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[179]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrma6i5z-6msx2jr\" data-page-width-em=\"33\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezgsOFxyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">8</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">8</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
