  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* Q1[λ1,λ2,λ3][M,n][u] = κ1^(u/h) q_n(u): the actual Baxter Q-function value, built from the\n   SAME QSolve cache (mutually consistent with τ by construction). *)\nClearAll[Q1];\nQ1[λ1_, λ2_, λ3_][M_, n_][u_] := Module[{q = QSolve[λ1, λ2, λ3][M, n]},\n  If[q === $Failed, $Failed, κ1^(u/h) qpoly[q, u]]];\n{Q1[1, 1, 1][1, 0][2], N[τ[1, 1, 1][1, 0][2], 10]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"598685\" data-output-id=\"134\" data-out-n=\"206\" data-sub-idx=\"3\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"40\" data-sub-start=\"5\" data-sub-end=\"5\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[206]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrma71w9-sj1enox\" data-page-width-em=\"33\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcey0xLjU1NTMwNDMxMzY1NzI2MTQ4ODQ1NDA2Ny0wLjEwNjA2ODE4NDY5NDgyMzEyNjQxNjQ5OVwsXG1hdGhybXtpfSwyLjQ1NTYwNDg3Mi0xLjE3MDgzMzg2NFwsXG1hdGhybXtpfVxyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">1.555304313657261488454067</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.106068184694823126416499</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2.455604872</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1.170833864</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=